---
title: Mango Chutney Glazed Curried Salmon with Sweet Potato Wedges and Baby Leaf & Lime Slaw
description: Salmon is a delicate and flavoursome fish, perfect for absorbing flavours such as the curry powder and mango chutney in this recipe. Paired with sweet potato wedges and a zingy slaw, it's a real catch!
